    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform, preserved in showroom condition. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 remains the centerpiece, utilizing eight individual throttle bodies to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and shows zero signs of subframe stress or bushing degradation. Preventative maintenance is exhaustive, including documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The factory finish remains flawless with no swirl marks, and the interior leather retains its original matte texture. A concours-ready specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
