      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with zero imperfections, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and the original factory scent remains. Every electronic component and comfort feature operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting every scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. This is a collector-grade investment for the most discerning buyer. No modifications, no stories\u2014just pure, untouched quality that must be seen in person to be fully appreciated.",
