    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains factory-spec with no subframe fatigue, benefiting from a rigid MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. The M-Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Finished in flawless Alpine White over a pristine Nappa leather interior, this vehicle retains its original VIN-matched panels and factory-spec bushings. Recent comprehensive service includes a VANOS system refresh and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with surgical precision. A rare opportunity to own a mechanically perfect icon of Bavarian engineering.",
